*Pizzamania*, the duo's singular album offering, was released in 1995 via [Cowboy](/Cowboy_Records) Records. Available in the standard formats of the time – Compact Disc (CD), Cassette (CS), and Long Play vinyl (LP) – it represented their complete artistic statement. While it managed to chart in Australia, reaching #141 on the [ARIA Charts](/ARIA_Charts), this position suggests it didn't quite capture the broader commercial imagination there, perhaps a testament to the album format's challenge for dance acts whose strength often lay in individual, impactful singles.

